{"tid":2305730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（Black Widow) 俄紅髮女一戰成名！爆打2百公斤壯男","createTime":"2020-11-30T01:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T09:02:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"768b0d6b76267514c0e446902c30c0fcfbdc6e19","tid":2305730,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbor.forbes.com/thumbor/711x402/https://specials-images.forbesimg.com/imageserve/5de65de0755ebf0006fc0705/960x0.jpg?fit=scale\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbor.forbes.com%2Fthumbor%2F711x402%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fspecials-images.forbesimg.com%2Fimageserve%2F5de65de0755ebf0006fc0705%2F960x0.jpg%3Ffit%3Dscale&h=72fe3b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誰說格鬥場上最大隻、最重的勝算大？這位俄羅斯女悍將的表現就足以證明一切，近日在俄羅斯某一場ＭＭＡ綜合格鬥比賽中，重達240公斤的男子就被62公斤的俄羅斯女翻轉局勢，甚至最後被女方壓在地上狂打27下後腦，不到3分鐘的影片立刻掀起外界熱議。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，240公斤的壯男齊斯捷科夫（Grigory Czystjakov）整整是紅髮女瑪德齊克（Darina Madziuk）體重的４倍，但瑪德齊克完全不畏懼，一開始就利用敏捷之姿，不斷展開攻擊，好幾次都擊中齊斯捷科夫的頭部，沒想到齊斯捷科夫完全打不退，步步把女方逼退到籠邊，隨即利用龐大身體壓制住，接著鎖喉攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n僵持大約半分鐘，裁判才趕快將雙方分開，重新比賽，怎料兩人靠近後一陣拳打，瑪德齊克再次正面擊中齊斯捷科夫的鼻子、臉部，沒想到男方疑似想靠身體壓制，結果換得重心不穩，直接撲倒在地，瑪德齊克眼見機會，直接壓在背上狂打後腦勺，大約揮出27下拳擊，齊斯捷科夫隨後宣布投降。<br />\n<br />\n然而，這影片不僅吸引俄羅斯圈內人關注，就連各種社群平台都有網友紛紛轉傳，大多人認為此賽事證明了在MMA比賽上「體型並不重要」，但也有人指出致勝關鍵就在於「訓練」，一位長期擁有良好訓練的拳擊手，絕對能夠打贏飲食不健康，且沒有任何技巧可言的胖子，也讓紅髮女一戰成名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E7%B4%85%E9%AB%AE%E5%A5%B3-%E6%88%B0%E6%88%90%E5%90%8D-%E7%88%86%E6%89%932%E7%99%BE%E5%85%AC%E6%96%A4%E5%A3%AF%E7%94%B7-010051977.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%25AB%25AE%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2590%258D-%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2589%25932%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%2596%25A4%25E5%25A3%25AF%25E7%2594%25B7-010051977.html&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=76483e39\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%84%E7%B4%85%E9%AB%AE%E5%A5%B3-%E6%88%B0%E6%88%90%E5%90%8D-%E7%88%86%E6%89%932%E7%99%BE%E5%85%AC%E6%96%A4%E5%A3%AF%E7%94%B7-010051977.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TJMfK7UXOKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTJMfK7UXOKk&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=c4234068\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TJMfK7UXOKk</a>"},{"pid":"0a97189a1a29379f893f3379c42c8ff03300a65c","tid":2305730,"uid":23445,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:01:21.000Z","msg":"成個波咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0c3f747cb4cd5ea0dc41192e0c5be16eafd82f","tid":2305730,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"Big Mac"},{"pid":"06d801f56bb0abb0964a9ba8cce780f18a69b473","tid":2305730,"uid":21141,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"最後張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa66c458e1fe7f3ebd59a6c160af3f920e88a6af","tid":2305730,"uid":75196,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"06d801f56bb0abb0964a9ba8cce780f18a69b473","tid":2305730,"uid":21141,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"最後張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9814e169122a05f9de0135f10680ca8e9422c14f","tid":2305730,"uid":16981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"768b0d6b76267514c0e446902c30c0fcfbdc6e19","tid":2305730,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T01:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbor.forbes.com/thumbor/711x402/https://specials-images.forbesimg.com/imageserve/5de65de0755ebf0006fc0705/960x0.jpg?fit=scale\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https